data.name: Spicy Chickpea and Spinach Stir-Fry
data.quickTastyDescription: A quick, healthy, and spicy chickpea and spinach stir-fry packed with flavor and nutrients!
detailedCookingInstructions: Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.
Add minced garlic and saut√© for 1 minute until fragrant.
Add the canned chickpeas (drained and rinsed) to the skillet.
Stir in red chili flakes, salt, and pepper, cooking for about 5 minutes.
Add fresh spinach and cook until wilted, about 3-4 minutes.
Remove from heat and drizzle with lemon juice before serving.
